videos.description: Shai Gileous-Alexander drops a dime to Tai Wynyard who finishes with the easy dunk for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Wynyard throws down the flush

videos.description: New Yankees manager Aaron Boone reacts to the news that his team is trying to trade for Giancarlo Stanton.
videos.headline: Aaron Boone says nothing official on Stanton front yet

videos.description: Kentucky head coach John Calipari says that PJ Washington will be one of the best players in the country by the end of the season.
videos.headline: Calipari has high praise for Washington

videos.description: Hamidou Diallo hits the transition three for the Wildcats in the second half.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Diallo drains 3-pointer

videos.description: A big PJ Washington block leads to an easy bucket for Hamidou Diallo on the offensive end for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Washington denies Monmouth

videos.description: Kentucky head coach John Calipari explains why his team still has a ton of learning to do.
videos.headline: Calipari breaks down freshmen growing pains

videos.description: Hamidou Diallo scores 23 points and PJ Washington adds 20 as the Wildcats roll 93-76.
videos.headline: Kentucky cruises past Monmouth
